Jessica Cunningham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessica_Cunningham 0 Jessica Cunningham (born March 1987) is a businesswoman, actress, model and television personality, best known for competing in the 2016 series of The Apprentice, coming fourth. She is also known for her appearance as a contestant on Celebrity Big Brother 19. She is the owner of the online fashion company ProdigalFox and the operations director for a PR and marketing agency.
